Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.29,0:00:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.97,0:00:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受不了了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.28,0:00:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活不下去的人就是廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.24,0:00:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了羅蘭德 變強吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.92,0:00:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的存在意義 就只有這一條
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.14,0:00:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.64,0:00:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.93,0:00:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當心我打飛你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.49,0:01:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多人想活下去卻丟了性命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.19,0:01:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少在這裡撒嬌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.48,0:01:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我不想再看到…大家死去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.58,0:01:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還不是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.22,0:01:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.60,0:01:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 握緊我的手絕對不要放開
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:06.98,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}眠り解きあぐねて　君を見失い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:06.98,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}漫长沉睡中醒来 却发现失去了你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.12,0:02:11.98,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}壊したくなる今すべて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.12,0:02:11.98,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}此刻恨不能破坏一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.06,0:02:20.49,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}望む言葉が二度と聞けないなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.06,0:02:20.49,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}若再也听不到 那令人心动的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.00,0:02:26.74,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}命さえ無為に差し出すでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.00,0:02:26.74,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}我宁愿徒然付出生命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.67,0:02:34.27,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}消えそうな輝きへと寄り添う想い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.67,0:02:34.27,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}心绪飘向那若隐若现的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.72,0:02:40.99,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}孤独だよ　私の元にも朝日がくるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.72,0:02:40.99,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}一阵孤独 是否我亦能拥有明日朝阳？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.40,0:02:48.45,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}答えて…ふたりを繋ぐ愛があると
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.40,0:02:48.45,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}告诉我 我们之间还有爱相连
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.65,0:02:54.97,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}招かれた絶望の果てに立ち向かう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.65,0:02:54.97,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}让我能直面眼前那无尽绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.26,0:03:01.99,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}産まれて滅びる人の意識こそが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.26,0:03:01.99,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}正是生而即逝的人之意识
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.31,0:03:12.59,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}未来を選び　鍵を開ける
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.31,0:03:12.59,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}才能选择未来 打开那心锁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}奈爾法皇國 城塞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.95,0:03:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}城內 寶物庫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.63,0:03:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.78,0:03:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就說 這裡沒有勇者遺物？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.20,0:03:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都建了個這麼嚴密的堡壘來藏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為一定是勇者遺物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這藏的居然是逃稅的記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匪夷所思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.11,0:03:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況我大致理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.84,0:03:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 你有什麼遺言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.61,0:04:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀 刀下留人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能有勇者遺物的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.77,0:04:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}絕不放手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.19,0:04:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.72,0:04:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個堡壘的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和文獻記載的勇者之劍沉睡之地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.59,0:04:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一點點偏差
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.41,0:04:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢 我們昨天不是有露營嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在森林裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.88,0:04:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實…那一帶就是地圖上有記號的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.92,0:04:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 然而你卻沒告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.27,0:04:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因 因為
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.51,0:04:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看那片沒插著勇者之劍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.59,0:04:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說明是有人拔走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者埋地下了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要挖掘幾千年前的遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.95,0:04:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也太麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說你不想幹？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說那啥對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.98,0:04:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呃不不不要殺我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 剛才就在那裡鬼鬼祟祟的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.76,0:04:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.84,0:04:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.49,0:04:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要襲擊能不能趕緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:04:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪斯伊哥哥小動作太多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.97,0:05:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不被發現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.35,0:05:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 怎麼怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還用問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.52,0:05:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 討厭 討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.09,0:05:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 財寶就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方好像很強
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備隨時逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.44,0:05:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 斯伊哥哥都二十六歲了還沒有生活能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.21,0:05:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為作家只會成天白日做夢還要我來養活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐我十四歲還沒戀愛結婚就要衰老腐爛了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可傷腦筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望庫能獲得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.86,0:05:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,財寶見者有份 能不能分我們一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.63,0:05:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當是庫的嫁妝 還請幫個忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有空隙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.32,0:05:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.81,0:05:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個財寶都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.13,0:05:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你把財寶藏哪兒去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.21,0:06:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就沒有這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？那你們來這兒幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.54,0:06:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了找勇者遺…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.82,0:06:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是奉奈爾法皇國國王機密特令而來的監察官
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.71,0:06:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那我們待這兒也沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 斯伊哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.13,0:06:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾二位了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.09,0:06:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈爾法的監察官啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.43,0:06:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs40}奈爾法皇國 旅館
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.13,0:06:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.00,0:06:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利雷 你不舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像沒怎麼吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.36,0:06:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.61,0:06:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來到這鎮上以後 完全沒有成果
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:07:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些破忌者 要能在哪兒華麗地用個魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就該有消息了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.66,0:07:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是在外國這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅蘭德的魔法不都洩露了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.51,0:07:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穆說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.88,0:07:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法的秘密為他國所知
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能會導致羅蘭德的滅亡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破忌者的存在就是這麼危險
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.45,0:07:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.30,0:07:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為習得魔法之人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻未經許可出逃外國的破忌者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追擊破忌者的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左右著國家的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.27,0:07:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此席恩陛下才親授此任
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.43,0:07:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚴肅的話題到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來點甜點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好好吃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.67,0:07:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.05,0:08:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可愛呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.57,0:08:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長那陶醉其中的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.49,0:08:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 您怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪拉赫戲弄隊長啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是你先說的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能像這樣和大家一起開心地吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太高興了 忍不住就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…打擾各位用餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.59,0:08:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你們在收集破忌者的情報？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們見過兩個像是破忌者的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.53,0:08:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請詳細跟我說說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲奧爾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.32,0:08:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}羅蘭德帝國 墓地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:08:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉我來遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我能力不足
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誇下海口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.87,0:09:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連本國的貴族都…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了 改改這毛病吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.01,0:09:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是菲奧爾·福克爾的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.22,0:09:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾絲莉娜·福克爾小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.74,0:09:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您別露出這樣的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄長會傷心的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄長他很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.40,0:09:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠為陛下效勞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說非常幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄長寄給我的多少封信中…都是這樣寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.03,0:10:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs40}奈爾法皇國 森林
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.44,0:10:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那對兄妹說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納是給那狂躁症壞女人抓住了什麼把柄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.20,0:10:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫不知情地被煽動利用了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠拯救萊納的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.05,0:10:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.74,0:10:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請下指示
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.59,0:10:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.23,0:10:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 我用魔法牽制
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.82,0:10:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穆掩護我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.19,0:10:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盧克 拉赫 利雷用劍攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.20,0:11:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封住破忌者的戰鬥能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行俘獲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.44,0:11:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.06,0:11:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 作戰開始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.07,0:11:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納 我這就來救你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.64,0:11:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾所求雷鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.18,0:11:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.38,0:11:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.28,0:11:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:11:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識這小姑娘嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.74,0:12:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧 你還想不起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.94,0:12:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是蜜爾可啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.96,0:12:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喏 就是一個孤兒院的蜜爾可
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.67,0:12:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.91,0:12:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.10,0:12:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.49,0:12:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說好要結婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結婚？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.25,0:12:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 你竟然從小就以結婚為誘餌欺騙少女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.27,0:12:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 如果那約定是真事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想和萊納結婚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是約定 也是小時候的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.56,0:12:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 能以這種形式重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.75,0:12:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是命運的紅線相連…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而重逢的往日少年
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.52,0:12:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經成長為稀世的變態
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 成長為變態…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.09,0:12:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你不要隨便加入奇怪的旁白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是助人為樂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.36,0:13:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為你帶來不幸的紅線
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.98,0:13:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我連同這傢伙的脖子一同斬斷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊 萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.17,0:13:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.74,0:13:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 不陪你們玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.29,0:13:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不回去幹活 天都黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你們等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.20,0:13:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納 萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說明明是奉席恩之命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼還要被追殺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.86,0:13:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋找遺物是機密任務
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.34,0:13:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指示沒有傳到最下層吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.39,0:13:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.33,0:13:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,複寫眼也看不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.09,0:13:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有被施加過某種力量的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 就是這股勁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 拉赫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是奈爾法軍的巡邏警備隊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是大聲喊 說不定他們會來救我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.98,0:14:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們追擊破忌者是有奈爾法許可的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.48,0:14:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是證明身份要花時間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破忌者們會逃跑的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 他們肯定在找萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.37,0:14:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得保護他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜爾可…隊長？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.11,0:14:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次…這次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輪到我救萊納了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.60,0:14:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上 上廁所！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你們把女孩子骨碌骨碌捆起來難道不覺得害臊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.36,0:15:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子有很多不方便的事啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.62,0:15:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.61,0:15:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那不是羅蘭德的魔法 電光嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是暗庭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止空氣振動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.53,0:15:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓聲音無法傳達的簡單魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.63,0:15:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最適合擾亂戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.51,0:15:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混賬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.12,0:15:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋萊納 為什麼要來救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.64,0:16:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家特地製造機會讓你逃的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.10,0:16:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 特地來救你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.36,0:16:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有點洩氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.02,0:16:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 您沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.94,0:16:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.30,0:16:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若要分心保護過去被你拋棄的女人以及那些男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可對付不了這麼多人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.41,0:16:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰拋棄人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.73,0:16:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拿著勇者遺留的劍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.20,0:16:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就說你就是勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是勇者就馬上給我想點辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.57,0:16:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼歪理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.49,0:16:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說這玩意要怎麼運作還…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻給我查
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.63,0:16:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全 一點也看不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:16:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.23,0:17:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說 這種情況下怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解析得出啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.92,0:17:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.02,0:17:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納 你做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.24,0:17:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤 撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.32,0:17:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.87,0:17:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是傳說中的勇者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 怎麼看都是龍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.85,0:17:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 總之
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:18:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把那散發無意義的危險氣場的龍收起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.90,0:18:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼收
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧 就這麼把龍置之不理了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.30,0:18:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 拿出來的東西要收好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是常識啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.72,0:18:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…沒資格被你們稱作隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 我那時…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.83,0:18:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只想著這次要救萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了這個 寧願捨棄一切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.34,0:18:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這等於背叛了最愛的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.83,0:18:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜爾可隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您別露出這樣的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.69,0:18:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.69,0:19:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這支小隊編成那天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.27,0:19:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜爾可·卡拉德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.68,0:19:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追擊破忌者的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.63,0:19:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屬下鄭重接受
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.70,0:19:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你確定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.80,0:19:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.73,0:19:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是殺害過去同胞的骯髒任務
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後 也有可能因此被人歧視
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.25,0:19:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝您的關心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.44,0:19:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我不在乎受傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.49,0:19:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經一度放棄生存
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.51,0:19:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避痛苦的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋求解脫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.40,0:19:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 一個我青梅竹馬的男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.27,0:19:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給了我生存的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想向他報恩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.95,0:20:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並保護讓我邂逅了他的羅蘭德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.74,0:20:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.95,0:20:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將引以為榮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.37,0:20:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,執行追擊破忌者的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.04,0:20:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時 我們就下了決心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.43,0:20:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要相信蜜爾可隊長 一直跟隨您
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.33,0:20:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.64,0:20:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要做自己認為正確的事就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.67,0:20:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您若犯了錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.14,0:20:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會為您糾正
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.64,0:20:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.18,0:20:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都站在您這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.29,0:20:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是我們的隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.48,0:20:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後再一起開心地吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.73,0:20:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.52,0:20:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一家人…
